{"tid":372175,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"超狂抗日神劇 間諜名單上全是麻藥搜查官AV女優","createTime":"2017-08-24T07:12:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T07:23:32.000Z","uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"04fedc42307382d35f6d2c08c6b9c9da29db8f56","tid":372175,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:12:55.000Z","msg":"超狂抗日神劇 間諜名單上全是AV女優<br />\n2017年08月21日 16:21  陳慶餘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2017-08-21/656/20170821003978.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2017-08-21%2F656%2F20170821003978.jpg&h=4d59c05e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西野翔（左圖）出現在抗日電影的間諜名單上（右圖），讓不少網友笑翻（翻攝推特、微博）<br />\n<br />\n中國大陸近五年來吹起抗日劇風潮，但卻因為不少劇情內容太過於誇張，而被不少網友開玩笑酸是「抗日神劇」。近日就有一組抗日電影的劇照截圖在網路上瘋傳，原來是有眼尖的網友發現，在這部電影中出現的日本間諜名字，竟全是知名的AV女優。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2017-08-21/656/20170821003841.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2017-08-21%2F656%2F20170821003841.jpg&h=84598c8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相關截圖在網路上瘋傳（翻攝豆瓣電影）<br />\n<br />\n這部在2016年發表的電影《百家拳之津門八卦掌》，是在描述一段發生於抗日戰爭爆發前夕，一名武林宗師伍皓東與民間藝人梅來寶之間英雄相惜，並且共同除暴安良的故事，但令人感到傻眼的是，電影中伍皓東在殺掉一名日本電報員後，奪走了一本寫滿日本間諜名字的小冊子，但沒想到上面寫的「西野翔、小川あさ美、かすみ果穂、かすみりさ」竟全是AV女優，最後一行出現的名字「しょかつりょう」更是諸葛亮，讓網友不滿的吐槽這部電影「到底是在汙辱誰的智商」、「滿分五顆星我只給一顆，這顆還是給裡面寫滿AV女優名字的小冊子」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2017-08-21/656/20170821003954.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2017-08-21%2F656%2F20170821003954.jpg&h=3400fd97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網友發現這些AV女優都演過「搜查官」系列的作品（翻攝推特）<br />\n<br />\n漫畫家韋宗成也在臉書分享該截圖，讓不少看到的台灣網友笑翻，紛紛留言表示「男精大屠殺的犯罪名單」、「名單上的都是優秀的騎兵將領」、「這一看就知道是老江湖了」、「抗日神劇導演嘴巴上抗日，身體很誠實」、「拿到麻藥搜查官的名單嗎」。"},{"pid":"5f1f8f30fa65eb05ba2a3eea463aee99650bedc7","tid":372175,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:16:44.000Z","msg":"小川あさ美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ad1f08e6fe425224efcaa73a49c6c95868e438","tid":372175,"uid":49197,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:18:33.000Z","msg":"男精大屠殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc36b0a0155538db3dd8b1f5b7371dd01e4961b9","tid":372175,"uid":74986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:22:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男精大屠殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b49f281eecba973e01f60b2dbd0be87e0bfd11","tid":372175,"uid":41076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:22:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>男精大屠殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da850c4909d74ec7efa3e9915b7f0d88f988202","tid":372175,"uid":80035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}